assets.description:
Designed by the award winning Bob Schmidt, this symbol of ecumenical unity portrays the star of David, the star and cresent, and the cross, depending on what angle it is viewed from. Shown at an exhibit in 1998 at the Hopkins Center for the Arts, it is now available online in digital form.

Like this model, but need something a bit different? I take commissions! http://peripheralarbor.com/commission/
